DreamLite Low-VRAM ComfyUI Nodes

This project provides ComfyUI wrappers and low-VRAM inference utilities for
local DreamLite installations.

The bundled `infer_base_offload.py` script is derived from DreamLite inference
code and retains the upstream Apache-2.0 license header from ByteDance Ltd.

DreamLite, ComfyUI, model checkpoints, and upscaler checkpoints are separate
projects with their own licenses and must be obtained separately by users.
